//                       в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ   в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
            display-name = "Config";
            bindings = <
   &kp ESC      &kp C_PREV   &kp C_PP     &kp C_NEXT    &kp C_MUTE    &kp DEL       &trans       &trans       &trans       &trans       &trans        &bt BT_CLR
   &kp TAB      &kp C_BRI_DN &kp C_VOL_DN &kp C_VOL_UP  &kp C_BRI_UP  &trans        &trans       &trans       &trans       &trans       &bt_win       &bt_mac
   &trans       &trans       &caps_word   &kp INS       &kp PSCRN     &trans        &trans       &bt_3        &bt_4        &bt_5        &trans        &trans
                                          &kp LCTRL     &kp LSHFT     &kp SPACE     &kp BSPC     &to DEF      &trans
